template.name: SAF Basic Integra-W template V1.0 for Zabbix 6.0

trigger.expression: max(/SAF Basic Integra-W template V1.0 for Zabbix 6.0/icmpping,#3)=0
trigger.name: Unavailable by ICMP ping
trigger.description: Last three attempts returned timeout. Please check device connectivity.

trigger.expression: min(/SAF Basic Integra-W template V1.0 for Zabbix 6.0/icmppingloss,5m)>{$ICMP_LOSS_WARN} and min(/SAF Basic Integra-W template V1.0 for Zabbix 6.0/icmppingloss,5m)<100
trigger.name: High ICMP Loss

dependency.name: Unavailable by ICMP ping
dependency.expression: max(/SAF Basic Integra-W template V1.0 for Zabbix 6.0/icmpping,#3)=0

trigger.expression: avg(/SAF Basic Integra-W template V1.0 for Zabbix 6.0/icmppingsec,5m)>{$ICMP_RESPONSE_TIME_WARN}
trigger.name: High ICMP Response Time

dependency.name: High ICMP Loss
dependency.expression: min(/SAF Basic Integra-W template V1.0 for Zabbix 6.0/icmppingloss,5m)>{$ICMP_LOSS_WARN} and min(/SAF Basic Integra-W template V1.0 for Zabbix 6.0/icmppingloss,5m)<100

dependency.name: Unavailable by ICMP ping
dependency.expression: max(/SAF Basic Integra-W template V1.0 for Zabbix 6.0/icmpping,#3)=0

trigger.expression: (last(/SAF Basic Integra-W template V1.0 for Zabbix 6.0/integraWifPortAdminStatus_LAN2,#1)<>last(/SAF Basic Integra-W template V1.0 for Zabbix 6.0/integraWifPortAdminStatus_LAN2,#2))=1
trigger.name: LAN port administrative status changed

trigger.expression: (last(/SAF Basic Integra-W template V1.0 for Zabbix 6.0/integraWifPortAdminStatus_MNG,#1)<>last(/SAF Basic Integra-W template V1.0 for Zabbix 6.0/integraWifPortAdminStatus_MNG,#2))=1
trigger.name: MNG port administrative status changed

item.name: Data Acquire Status
item.description: This is the current status of modem data acquire when queried modem status.

valuemap.name: SAF INTEGRA G Modem acquire staus

trigger.expression: last(/SAF Basic Integra-W template V1.0 for Zabbix 6.0/SAF-INTEGRAW-MIB_integraWmodemAcquireStatus)=1
trigger.name: Modem Acquire Status in Progress

item.name: FEC Load
item.description: Decoder stress or FEC load value

trigger.expression: last(/SAF Basic Integra-W template V1.0 for Zabbix 6.0/SAF-INTEGRAW-MIB_integraWmodemFECload)>=80
trigger.name: FEC load high

item.name: Modem Rx Capacity

item.name: Modem Tx Capacity
item.description: Tx ethernet capacity in kilobits per second

valuemap.name: SAF INTEGRA G Rx level state

trigger.recovery_expression: last(/SAF Basic Integra-W template V1.0 for Zabbix 6.0/SAF-INTEGRAW-MIB_integraWradioRxLevelState)=1
trigger.name: Rx level status alarm

trigger.expression: last(/SAF Basic Integra-W template V1.0 for Zabbix 6.0/SAF-INTEGRAW-MIB_integraWradioTemperature)>=100 and last(/SAF Basic Integra-W template V1.0 for Zabbix 6.0/SAF-INTEGRAW-MIB_integraWradioTemperature)<=-40

trigger.expression: last(/SAF Basic Integra-W template V1.0 for Zabbix 6.0/SAF-INTEGRAW-MIB_integraWsysCPUload)>95
